2000-02-09  Christopher James Lahey  <clahey@helixcode.com>

	* configure.in: Add new Makefiles to Makefile list.

	* e-util/Makefile.am: Add canvas utilities to libeutil.

	* widgets/e-text/Makefile.am: Build libetext.

