	* camel/providers/mbox/camel-mbox-folder.c (_get_message_count): 
	implemented.

	* camel/providers/mbox/camel-mbox-summary.c (camel_mbox_save_summary): 
	(camel_mbox_load_summary): save/load the next uid. 

